sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as Transfer - Customer - Client
    participant Gateway as API Gateway
    participant TransactionS as Transaction Service
    participant DB_Trans as Transactions DB

    Client->>Gateway: GET /transactions/account/{accountId}
    Gateway->>TransactionS: Forward get transactions request
    TransactionS->>DB_Trans: Query transactions by account ID
    DB_Trans-->>TransactionS: Transaction records
    TransactionS-->>Gateway: Transaction history
    Gateway-->>Client: 200 OK (transaction list)
